Innovation Leadership (R&D, pilots, partnerships and IP)
- Product and product‑technology R&D: Altria is investing in smoke‑free and alternative nicotine delivery technologies (including flavor delivery and nicotine incorporation for reduced‑risk product lines), and has active patents and IP filings in aerosol and carrier materials (indicative of product‑technology innovation, not necessarily low‑carbon process tech) ([altria patents](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFwpZSsgOosnDJevB219RrkDPdEfOaPMNeH6l7az_q8VN5pXBoGG-4tcb6Q-Hj6DhRaX_C-Uow4oJqx5cwZcwdZhSomy9DgQM2hPpkcwWOLUC-0PWBYKQxwu7hBFgliOeL1r-S9MYyuvCEbbrRPI0NzZtmwZZyhGALc); [patents list](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHIuOV9PhmngICcXUkWzTMiXeWh8OJ2WbezgmW_KAOoUKELOkP5flam5VJ3As97Bh4GOJGqPwFpw0ixhYWeqKR9upV8Cms3Iq7AVM2T6oLRhGEt3QoXttxf8krnEe3RoLAxi2tN8f3Vcw2ufoZGgJ3qO9jK_IBO3W55); [altria R&D investments](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGW1LAbSZDVZoPnUVYRJnlNAecBrcsaSM0x20ItQVTWmyXWskqBWidZ5oUNjA-91WWwYN2n39J3GNd219wRq0y4Vu1p2fOiZKjk_GWc3Dn2AdY4H1sdg30BSxo5QcvcVhoNO1FOX3G0JRORAlkJ_wOLQ88xfnuFQn4trwa6DbEGG6MLpNucHx-S71hOHpDljJJbhVkNbcopyRi6Jj18CYaeb-w-T_OotcUqDSrbg1yoWFYY-XzRYOBiya4CqTwl4SaLvatWpON7wpyB3oM=)).  
