Measurable Impact (documented environmental & business impacts)
- Renewable energy impact: VPPA estimated to reduce ~283,000 tCO2e/year and deliver ~400,000 MWh/year of renewable generation to the grid (equivalent comparisons in filings and press coverage) ([altria](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEQxiTWVhgC-o8d3mzKc_-fc3kmmeBhKgSagkmeodr9zHf3u7pzZxIJxhz9YUOHsucvtkG6soAWH1H7-S0IgXPvFDkliELHs_ak8On_Rdu9YN_QNdGKGsx7Wv6CxkngoYZJCwUA5UzaUX6jx-LPwR8QMbSw9EHXmhKLLEv6-37J7X_I6rexuux3bIzCF9IIuozSvBNoHOrGYCY4L5mg7jGfTsMjnVoO5OTII7NHiI6es4C-91LOyab-UcN5f8x14LTJRs9T8MUg4tHdkPX37CSyfOpI3eGYbDKobx-65DSJ4mpU4RzKISW0u4BDDsiyzHPW0_0=); [tobaccoreporter](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCXZ4dMO6JDiv68kSghuMAN7kKwuAp5Le8iuHITGG5FNU8bmOEAgysCj4EdZ3yUbXSEefOx8gfy4cnFvFTRsTmMDN6cuYE_UkGHLwS9J1t0rdsgvP7rvkprHMvoYjRQ0LwBsCudj1JOJKcNi-tNYlKq4NmJUCKmBMgYbFWEh8yyuRKxltrRuem8BojdPVt-AM=); [energychoicematters](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEPfeqTSV6gX4xVNXoVM4SbmGRxMxQl-1XUbbFT6v4AMX81eZjWwD8Mi0PCto52vHDOnaVm2ueSj_IYxFyV6ti3qpIyg5pOPndJRMMr6e-PU2xF1HUI68uJb97s0it19qhTiFX6JjnJjYn8xSBCIPuabamX2w==)).  
- Emissions targets & progress: Altria reported that it essentially achieved its earlier 2030 targets years ahead of schedule (the company resubmitted and in 2024 had SBTi‑validated updated 2030 targets aligned to 1.5°C pathways) and has set aggressive 2030 targets (Scope 1+2 reduction 90%; Scope 3 FLAG 72%; Scope 3 energy/industrial 90%) and a 2050 net‑zero value‑chain goal ([altria SBTi/targets submission & validation](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBtJTq8IvFER_wEuWzRIEoeVJTzCopNYIvWQCk2doPuRqM8APLTvcUgq2oEbjQY9bjo-9ZqGyIh129bpnTJ5pe4eF8HV9SMn9rkXDEigK6Llx4RRf3MR1-7Ios4Da-mR5yIkqV1qX5v6UAbHu-1uxlDZ9uqgJ0m5aLnx9GyMBtwBamKijMPWk=); [altria](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHoUif25fD91ASgobn-wOCpGk1ogp9GkLXbNGexHVO38gDf20g7Iy3abeToHCwd4KAxwIPDM8_TAd4PfVigNuXcNa7SVi9Rq3trj4zGrQBVLS8gw0_cAZrWzif_m2mAQKU0eZTgoHCPpe13wibo8oceiDpR17XHgw==); [altria](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF6niKq3Cm3yOEjEDciROtdrSN-w0isXeKv3MVOgl8STKElJr0AYzYTwE1NMYzCrqNkGY2a9G0aGTN4PkQV0C9URGs0nOfmrf2hEp-vH86GX4zGiD7Rw72lWGIkAhL06CNLUA8n0PPtzktJ828GgMwcFPm8CaaZIot9HjqWXF3is9kQkZRQwJhzpLk=)).  
