- Disclosure & ratings: Altria aligns reporting to GRI/SASB/TCFD, responds to CDP and (in 2024) reported CDP results of B for Climate, B for Forests and A‑ for Water Security — indicating materially credible disclosure but not top‑tier (Triple‑A) CDP performance ([altria CDP scores](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGTE5RT9bJMZkA59FvuRgguLmp0mVBrTzoKaZoy3d0gEyuQC-vhPjaFPGCLNcOOYU4Isy3oSBo5lo4TCcJ3XLtldVgaGmVLDBUW1WGgmxt1rS3Mxngl65rPW9YpxAn_YcVcD2qrdKgrnzk2854yl2OeGhqSC4Zu9tOeUUQk5Zm--SwTI3QHjzJkFy-8UVdU_8o=); [altria reporting TCFD/GRI](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBtJTq8IvFER_wEuWzRIEoeVJTzCopNYIvWQCk2doPuRqM8APLTvcUgq2oEbjQY9bjo-9ZqGyIh129bpnTJ5pe4eF8HV9SMn9rkXDEigK6Llx4RRf3MR1-7Ios4Da-mR5yIkqV1qX5v6UAbHu-1uxlDZ9uqgJ0m5aLnx9GyMBtwBamKijMPWk=)).  
